@jmagne So I'm confused here. The comment above says "trailer field ignored". I'm not entirely clear on how getSequence works, but if there was a trailer field, wouldn't it return an array of 4 DerValue elements?
In particular readVector(...) uses startLen as the initialize size of the vector, but it'll grow if there are four fields.
Shouldn't this read if (seq.length < 3 || seq.length > 4)?

